{"tid":1164330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭電訊商設備發現涉華為後門程式","createTime":"2019-05-21T03:52:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T13:20:44.000Z","uid":141151,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1457fe97028819900860f6b42814bfe3983ffb79","tid":1164330,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:52:57.000Z","msg":"荷蘭電訊商設備發現涉華為後門程式<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=348252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348252&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=899fe5c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348252&h=6be33be8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=348252</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】有報道指，荷蘭情報部門在當地一間主要電訊商的華為網絡設備內，發現後門程式，正調查中國有否藉此展開間諜活動。華為對報道表示驚訝，但指不會回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭《人民報》引述情報與安全總局消息人士指，當局在其中一間主要電訊商所使用的華為網絡設備中，發現後門程式，可能被用以查閱顧客資料，當局正調查中國政府有否藉此展開間諜活動。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭情報與安全總局表示，不回應有關報道。<br />\n<br />\n華為對報道表示驚訝，但指報道引述匿名消息，他們不會回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n《人民報》引述華為代表指，華為遵守所在國家法規，不容許他人利用華為設備從事威脅網絡安全活動。<br />\n<br />\n華為的5G技術被美國指可能危害網絡安全，華府一直游說歐洲國家在建設5G網絡時，不要使用華為的設備，其中英國政府早前開會，初步決定只在非核心部分容許使用華為產品。<br />\n<br />\n但英國軍情六處前處長迪爾洛夫警告，華為若透過5G產品控制資訊及通話，等同向一個國家行使權力，將對英國構成嚴重威脅，促請首相文翠珊重新考慮。<br />\n<br />\n首相府回應時表示，當局正研究最合適政策，有決定時會宣布。<br />\n<br />\n法國總統馬克龍表示，他不會向美國壓力屈服，禁止華為參與當地的5G網絡建設。<br />\n<br />\n德國總理默克爾則重申，柏林當局的政策是所有競投5G牌照的公司，都要符合當局定下的條件。"},{"pid":"7ce1d18e66af3f4099214b208febf74751f16934","tid":1164330,"uid":141151,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>行船爭解纜<br />\n後門佢裝先</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64bb59eb385cac72dd1ac3a325b691ad02bd59a","tid":1164330,"uid":104171,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:58:36.000Z","msg":"其實資料點都會查閱到架啦用咩都係架啦"},{"pid":"8d9b276e0bbdc50f42466e42490d1be409968a4f","tid":1164330,"uid":6752,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:00:17.000Z","msg":"《人民報》引述華為代表指，華為遵守所在國家法規，不容許<span style=\"color: red;\">他人</span>利用華為設備從事威脅網絡安全活動。<br />\n<br />\n得華為可以睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef23c2cfc620f374f4282424af6ad7e8fe37aaff","tid":1164330,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2d9f8b79cd67b6c65e869b6b19974367b0a7e1","tid":1164330,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8674f0e1c1d4d5392c7750fa02ec622b41bf7a","tid":1164330,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c64bb59eb385cac72dd1ac3a325b691ad02bd59a","tid":1164330,"uid":104171,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:58:36.000Z","msg":"其實資料點都會查閱到架啦用咩都係架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0d763699a129e929196403fd295660fdce045e","tid":1164330,"uid":141151,"l